df <- read.csv("GDIS_modify.csv", header=TRUE, sep=",", na.strings=" ")
df_mutate<-df %>%
  select(country,year,disastertype)
world_map<-map_data("world") %>%
  left_join(df_mutate,by=(c("region"="country")))
world_map %>%
  filter(year==2015) %>%
  group_by(disastertype,region)%>%
  mutate(count=n()) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x=long,y=lat,group=group))+geom_polygon(aes(fill=count),color="white")+facet_wrap(vars(disastertype))

library(countrycode)
  world_map$continent <- countrycode(sourcevar = world_map[, "region"],
                            origin = "country.name",
                            destination = "continent")

world_map %>%
  filter(year==2015) %>%
